### Step 1 - Register Admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Axiora Admin",
  "email": "admin@axiora.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

###

### Step 2 - Register Employee
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Roop Sai",
  "email": "roop@axiora.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "EMPLOYEE"
}

###

### Step 3 - Login (copy token to env file)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@axiora.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Step 4 - Create Goal for Employee (id: 2)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/goals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Improve Code Quality",
  "description": "Increase test coverage to 80%",
  "weightage": 100.00,
  "period": "2026-Q1",
  "assignedToId": 2
}

###

### Step 5 - Submit KPI for Goal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/kpis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "goalId": 1,
  "targetValue": 100.00,
  "actualValue": 95.00,
  "period": "2026-Q1",
  "notes": "Great progress on test coverage"
}

###

### Step 6 - Create Rule
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rules
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "High Achiever",
  "description": "Achievement greater than 90%",
  "operator": "GT",
  "thresholdValue": 90.00,
  "action": "ADD",
  "actionValue": 10.00,
  "priority": 1
}

###

### Step 7 - Run Evaluation for Employee
POST http://localhost:8080/api/evaluations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": 2,
  "period": "2026-Q1"
}

###

### Step 8 - Get Evaluation by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/evaluations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Step 9 - Get Evaluations by User
GET http://localhost:8080/api/evaluations/user/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}